text: Barney McLean (December 23, 1917 - July 19, 2005) was an American alpine skier. He competed in three events at the 1948 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1917 births Category:2005 deaths Category:American male alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of the United States Category:Alpine skiers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:People from Lander, Wyoming
